name: "no lo se rick"

Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
it looks like Ricardus stills in LA and has been visiting or trying to sell something at the most famous pawn shop but why is he wearing an Indiana t-shirt?
today our friend has been blessed with some of diewiththemostlikes's syrup and is still looking for his best halloween costume, c'mon ricardus decide once and for all!
